cat <<-EOS
Usage:	sub0 COMMAND

Commands:
  help                This screen
  console             Display the console that will watch for file changes and show live logs
  logs SUBSYSTEM      Display live the logs of the SUBSYSTEM (db/openresty/rabbitmq)
  resetdb             Reset the database schema and data
  watchfiles          Whatch for changes in sql/nginx/lua files and make them live


